<subSubSection id="C328ABCEFFB348027BB0FE7EFB014D79" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B8DF845FFB348027BB0FE7EFE954ED0" blockId="14.[189,310,430,456]" box="[189,310,430,456]" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">
<heading id="D0C54F29FFB348027BB0FE7EFE954ED0" bold="true" box="[189,310,430,456]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB348027BB0FE7EFE954ED0" bold="true" box="[189,310,430,456]" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8DF845FFB348027BB0FE0DFB014D79" blockId="14.[189,1399,477,609]" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">
Species with incomplete notauli like 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB34802797FFE0DFCA44EEF" authorityName="Fergusson" authorityYear="1985" box="[626,775,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atricornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB34802797FFE0DFCA44EEF" box="[626,775,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. atricornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB34802781BFE0DFC694EEF" box="[790,970,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavidicornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB34802781BFE0DFC694EEF" box="[790,970,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. flavidicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB3480278D4FE0DFBEE4EEF" authorityName="Belizin" authorityYear="1961" box="[985,1101,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paucus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB3480278D4FE0DFBEE4EEF" box="[985,1101,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. paucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB348027F8AFE0DFAAA4EEF" box="[1159,1289,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB348027F8AFE0DFAA64EEF" authorityName="Kovalev" authorityYear="1974" box="[1159,1285,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zaitzevi">A. zaitzevi</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
It can be distinguished from all these species by not having posteriorly defined carinae in the scutellar foveae and possessing incomplete interfoveal line (scutellar foveae always defined by a posterior carina and interfoveal line complete in 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB348027905FD97FD3F4D78" authorityName="Fergusson" authorityYear="1985" box="[520,668,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atricornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB348027905FD97FD3F4D78" box="[520,668,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. atricornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB3480279A7FD97FCFD4D79" box="[682,862,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavidicornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB3480279A7FD97FCFD4D79" box="[682,862,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. flavidicornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB348027866FD97FC7C4D78" authorityName="Belizin" authorityYear="1961" box="[875,991,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paucus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB348027866FD97FC7C4D78" box="[875,991,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. paucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB348027F15FD97FB324D78" authorityName="Kovalev" authorityYear="1974" box="[1048,1169,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="122" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zaitzevi">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB348027F15FD97FB324D78" box="[1048,1169,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="122">A. zaitzevi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
